WEBVTT

00:03:28.636 --> 00:03:31.329
huhifadhi seli zaidi ya
milioni mia moja tofauti.

00:03:31.848 --> 00:03:33.729
Pamoja na kufanana kijenetikia,

00:03:33.753 --> 00:03:36.462
kuna tofauti ndogo katika
saratani hizi tofauti

00:03:36.486 --> 00:03:39.343
inazozifanya zigeuke tofauti
kwa dawa tofauti.

00:03:39.367 --> 00:03:41.795
Hivyo hata kama una dawa yenye
kufanya kazi vizuri,

00:03:41.819 --> 00:03:43.554
ambayo huua karibia seli zote,

00:03:43.578 --> 00:03:46.768
kunauwezekano kwamba
kuna idadi ndogo ya seli

00:03:46.792 --> 00:03:48.566
ambayo ni sugu kwa dawa.

00:03:48.590 --> 00:03:50.612
Hii hatimaye ni idadi ya seli

00:03:50.636 --> 00:03:51.800
ambazo hurudi,

00:03:51.824 --> 00:03:53.142
na kumchukua tena mgonjwa.

00:03:53.887 --> 00:03:56.746
Sasa basi swali ni:
Tunafanyia nini taarifa hii?

00:03:56.770 --> 00:03:58.032
Chamsingi basi,

00:03:58.056 --> 00:04:02.926
Ni kutumia maboresho yote haya
ya kusisimua kwa tiba ya saratani mapema,